rawContent:
There are six factors identified by pioneering researcher Christina Maslach, PhD, that influence #burnout:
1️⃣ Work overload
2️⃣ Lack of control
3️⃣ Insufficient rewards
4️⃣ Breakdown of community
5️⃣ Sense of unfairness
6️⃣ Conflicting values

rawContent:
When we're #burntout, it's already too late to slow down. You need deep rest, entire days off. You also need to exit the cycle by doing some physical activity. 
Make sure you don't get to that point!
Take care of your whole self, which also includes your brain.
#burnout #phdlife

 ¿Sospechas que lo tienes?

👉 ¿Te has vuelto cínico o crítico en el trabajo?
👉 ¿Te arrastras al trabajo y tienes problemas para empezar?
👉 ¿Tus compañeros te dicen que estás insoportable?
👉 ¿Te cuesta comenzar?

¿Si? 
Puede ser burnout. 

¡Consulta!

To fix #overthinking caused by #burnout or #anxiety, you must first explore and resolve your emotions.
That's because your emotions happen first, and your thinking mind then follows, reflecting the tone of your emotions.
Heal your emotions & your thoughts will heal themselves.
